                <li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <main class="dog-care">
        <section class="care-intro">
            <h2>Dog Care Tips</h2>
            <p>Ensuring your dog is healthy and happy involves regular care and maintenance. Below are essential tips every dog owner should follow.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="care-tips">
            <div class="tip">
                <img src="/Images/feeding-icon.jpg" alt="Feeding">
                <h3>Feeding</h3>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                <p>Offer a balanced diet specific to your dog's age, size, and health needs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <img src="/Images/exercise-icon.jpg" alt="Exercise">
                <h3>Exercise</h3>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                <p>Provide regular exercise to keep your dog physically fit and mentally stimulated.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <img src="/Images/grooming-icon.jpg" alt="Grooming">
                <h3>Grooming</h3>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                <p>Regular grooming helps maintain your dog's coat and promotes bonding.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <img src="/Images/training-icon.jpg" alt="Training">
                <h3>Training</h3>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                <p>Basic obedience training is essential for a well-behaved dog and strengthens your bond.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <img src="/Images/healthcare-icon.jpg" alt="Healthcare">
                <h3>Healthcare</h3>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                <p>Regular vet check-ups and vaccinations are crucial for your dog's health and well-being.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="more-info">
            <h2>Learn More</h2>
            <p>For more detailed information on caring for your dog, visit our resources page or contact us directly.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn">Contact Us</a>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('footer') %>
